sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Feast Operator<br/>Controller
    participant Registry as Registry Service<br/>6570/6571 gRPC
    participant Online as Online Store<br/>6566/6567 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/SQLite<br/>5432/TCP or PVC
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Metrics as Metrics Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Operator: Flow 1: FeatureStore Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create FeatureStore CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>Service Account Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployments, Services, PVCs<br/>Auth: Service Account Token<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update FeatureStore status

    Note over MLApp,DB: Flow 2: Feature Retrieval (Online)
    MLApp->>Online: POST /online/features<br/>6566/TCP HTTP or 6567/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Configurable (RBAC/OIDC)
    Online->>DB: Query feature values<br/>PostgreSQL/SQLite protocol<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    DB-->>Online: Feature data
    Online-->>MLApp: JSON Response<br/>Low-latency features

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Feature Metadata Access
    User->>Registry: gRPC: GetFeatureView<br/>6570/TCP or 6571/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Configurable
    Registry->>DB: Read feature definitions<br/>File/SQL/S3 storage<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    DB-->>Registry: Feature metadata
    Registry-->>User: Feature definition

    Note over Operator,Metrics: Flow 5: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Metrics->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>Validate bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>Metrics: Token valid
    Metrics-->>Prometheus: Operator metrics (Prometheus format)
